												<a href="/index.php/energy/item/318-fukushima-evacuees-demand-compensation">Fukushima Evacuees  Demand Compensation</a>
																</h2>
								<ul>
												<li class="itemCategory"> <span>Published in</span> <a href="/index.php/energy/itemlist/category/14-general">General</a> </li>
																		<li class="itemAuthor"> Written by 
